      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": 54,
      "message": "could provide a constructor that takes a ToscaConceptIdentifierOptVersion, and possibly one that takes a ToscaConceptIdentifier.  That would have a secondary benefit of reducing this lambda to simply:\n\n  PapPolicyIdentifier::new",
      "author": {
